cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM

The paper deals with deep neural networks (DNNs) and their performance on ImageNet, which is a dataset of images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also discusses the decision-making process of DNNs, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The use of bag-of-feature models is related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper discusses the accuracy and performance of the models, which falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM).
